Name: Get the Banana
About the game: Get the Banana is a Sokoban-inspired game centered around two different but related characters: a monkey trapped in a research project involving a set of puzzles, and a research assistant helping to conduct the experiment. The game contains 12 puzzles involving pushable objects as well as doors, powered wires, fire and explosives, and more. Contents/Features: 12 puzzles, involving a variety of objects and tools An original story based around a team of researchers
